five sample opinions

[1] In modern times,ping-pong has always been associated with China, so I learned for the first time that Austria was the first to dominate. Looking back at history, I think Japanese ping-pong taught has had a major impact on society.                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                       
[2]                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                              
[3] I support his idea that the best way to win any game is never to think about the score. I think that it is true in other aspects, not only ping-pong as he says. People sometimes focus on the score but more important things is the step to the win. I guess the style of practice is also important and affects his learning. Since I had played ping-pong in junior high school, I never thought that the way to win is to never think about scores. I feel that the environment and the idea is to make people different like in his state between England and Japan. This is why I agree with his idea.
[4] I was so surprised by this story because I had the image that China’s players are playing an active role in the match these days. I also heard for the first time that the game lasted for over two hours. I think that it is good to have fun in the community without games, but I have to concentrate more on it at crucial moments. I think that we need to add contrast by fun and concentration, for example the exam and career event and interview in the future.                                                                                                                                    
[5] I think that his notice is very peaceful and considerate about other people. According to Italian news, sports festivals do not have prizes or ranking in kindergarten or elementary school. This is because, this event is not to decide children are valuable only by the ability of sports.However, I disagree about this idea because children have to get competition experience. Winning experience not also, losing experience needs children to grow up. So I believe that to compete is a good influence on our motivation.
